A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering skyscrapers are made of stacked, glowing code blocks in neon green and electric blue. In the foreground, a lone figure in a dark hoodie methodically dismantles a massive, chaotic tangle of luminescent wires and circuits, carefully sorting them into neat, organized bundles that glow with clean white light. The scene shows a stark contrast between the messy, sparking red-orange legacy systems on the left side and pristine, orderly blue-white structures emerging on the right. Rain falls through holographic grids, and the atmosphere is dense with fog and digital particles. The mood is determined yet hopeful, capturing the gradual transformation from chaos to order.
